headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Announces New Investor Relations Leader
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the appointment of Sara Walsh, CFA, to lead the Investor Relations team.

headline: 3 Reasons Investors Love Arthur J. Gallagher (AJG)
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher has gotten torched over the last six months - since August 2025, its stock price has dropped 27.9% to $215.29 per share. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
